  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个教育系统的数据同步流程图。核心是从Education_ClassroomService开始，它要访问Education_StudentDB。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U",
        "A1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Education_ClassroomService是用户入口，Education_StudentDB是数据库节点。那StudentDB这边还有别的交互吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U",
        "A1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，StudentDB这里有个工具节点H1，它也要访问A1。另外还有T1，Education_GradeSync，作为同步工具，也要连到A1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "H1",
        "A1",
        "T1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以H1和T1都是工具类节点，都指向A1。我注意到T1还回连到A1，形成双向关系。接下来流程怎么走？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T1",
        "A1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "从A1出来要做一个判断，D1，Education_LMS_Portal，检查是否需要走LMS门户流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A1",
        "D1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "D1是决策菱形。如果Yes的话怎么走？No的话呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Yes分支走C1，Education_GradeSync，然后直接回到Education_ClassroomService，也就是U。No分支走A2，Education_LMS_Portal。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D1",
        "C1",
        "U",
        "A2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了。D1的Yes分支到C1再到U，No分支到A2。A2是助手节点对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D1",
        "C1",
        "U",
        "A2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，A2是助手节点。从A2还要再做一次判断D2，Education_ClassroomService，检查是否需要额外数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A2",
        "D2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "D2也是决策点。Yes和No分别指向哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "D2的Yes分支走R1，Education_ContentCDN，然后到APPD。No分支直接到AT。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D2",
        "R1",
        "APPD",
        "AT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "R1是助手节点，APPD是应用节点。那APPD后面连到AT，Education_ContentCDN对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APPD",
        "AT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，APPD到AT。然后AT这里要分两种情况：Needs App Execution和No Execution Needed。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这两种情况都是AT出发的分支吗？最终汇聚到哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，AT分两支。Needs App Execution走APP_ACK，Education_GradeSync，然后到U2。No Execution Needed直接到U2。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AT",
        "APP_ACK",
        "U2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "U2是Education_LMS_Portal，和U一样都是用户节点。现在我来检查一下样式分类。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "样式方面，U和U2是user类，A1、A2、C1、R1还有AT是assistant类，D1和D2是decision类，APPD和APP_ACK是app类，T1和H1是tool类。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U",
        "U2",
        "A1",
        "A2",
        "C1",
        "R1",
        "AT",
        "D1",
        "D2",
        "APPD",
        "APP_ACK",
        "T1",
        "H1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "样式都设置好了。不过我发现一个问题，R1后面写的R2、CALL在图里没有出现，需要删掉吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "对，R2和CALL是多余的，删掉。还有class定义里那些不存在的节点都去掉。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R2",
        "CALL"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已清理。现在class assistant只包含A1、A2、C1、R1、AT。确认一下AT的归类，它确实是助手节点对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，AT是Education_ContentCDN，属于助手节点。整个流程再帮我过一遍：从U开始，经过A1，有H1和T1两个工具交互，然后D1判断，Yes走C1回U，No走A2到D2。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U",
        "A1",
        "H1",
        "T1",
        "D1",
        "C1",
        "A2",
        "D2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "D2的Yes分支是R1到APPD，然后APPD到AT。D2的No分支直接到AT。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D2",
        "R1",
        "APPD",
        "AT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 23,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，然后AT分Needs App Execution走APP_ACK到U2，或者No Execution Needed直接到U2。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AT",
        "APP_ACK",
        "U2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 24,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "有个细节，D1的Yes分支写的是C1到U，但U是Education_ClassroomService，U2是Education_LMS_Portal，这两个用户节点是不同的入口吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U",
        "U2",
        "C1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 25,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，U是课堂服务入口，U2是LMS门户入口。C1完成后回到课堂服务，而AT的最终输出是到LMS门户。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U",
        "U2",
        "C1",
        "AT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 26,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "理解了，两个不同的用户端。图已经完整了，所有节点和连线都对应上了。需要再调整什么吗？",
      "elements_involved": [],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
