      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "T1和H1都是连到A1，但方向都是单向的吧？T1那里你画的是双向？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T1",
        "A1",
        "H1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 28,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "我检查一下，代码里T1 -- A1是单向的，我重新确认一下连线方向。H1 -- A1也是单向。都修正为单向箭头。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T1",
        "A1",
        "H1"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 29,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好，现在对了。最后确认一下颜色：user是蓝色，assistant是绿色，decision是黄色，app是紫色，tool是橙色。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user",
