    {
      "turn_id": 30,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "全部确认。流程图已完成，从Education_ClassroomService出发，经过StudentDB、LMS判断、ContentCDN处理，最终到LMS门户或返回课堂服务，所有样式分类正确。",
